cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.SD, cs.CL 

This paper is primarily focused on cybersecurity and threat monitoring, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques, which could be classified under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the use of clustering algorithms and feature extraction could be categorized under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval), respectively. Finally, the paper involves the development of a monitoring system, which could be classified under cs.SD (Software Engineering).
